title: Mr Brooks [iPod] Great Quality
description:
I rip all my dvd&#039;s for iPods but at a higher bitrate then most (1400) because I also like to be able to play my iPod though my 50" TV with out a lot of lost quality. This also explains why most of my files are much larger then normal m4v movie files.

Because of the higher bitrate and larger file size your iPod will take a few seconds longer then normal to start playing the movie, this it perfectly normal.

Enjoy.
